lead_paragraph: Formula One world champion Nico Rosberg hailed Mercedes team mate Lewis Hamilton as one of the greatest drivers of all time on Wednesday but ruled out forging any friendly ties with the Briton as long as they raced each other.

headline.print_headline: Hamilton One of the Best, but No Friend: Rosberg
headline.main: Hamilton One of the Best, but No Friend: Rosberg
